cast.overview: Ethan and team take on their most impossible mission yet—eradicating 'The Syndicate', an International and highly-skilled rogue organization committed to destroying the IMF.
cast.title: Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation

details.biography: Saif Al-Warith (born 30th November, 1988) is a British stage, TV and film actor. Al-Warith is of Iraqi descent but was raised in the United Kingdom from the age of two months old. His name "Saif Al-Warith" when literally translated from Arabic to English means "The Sword which inherits all".
details.name: Saif Al-Warith
